First screen is the DecisionActivity

DecisionActivity: has two buttons Host and Client
    User decides what they want to be, from there we redirect their activity.

If HostActivity
    Turns on wifi tethering and setups local gateway server in the app for the web portal
    Enable temporary internet access for the web portal for the user the login too.
    Wait for user to login in sucessfully and recieve a response of OK from the server to allow internet access.
